      • getConstantDefinitions

        List<ConstantDefinition> getConstantDefinitions()
                                                throws GlueGenException
        Returns a list of ConstantDefinition, i.e. non-function-like and non-empty macros w/ constant-value, as derived during parsing.

        May return an empty list, in case this preprocessor does not store ConstantDefinitions.

        Throws:
        GlueGenException
